            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1626787001767-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the mushrooms are cooking, peel and roughly chop the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the<strong> butterbeans</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>veg stock mix</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1626787092146-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1626787092146-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1626787092146-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1626787092146-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1626787092146-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half</strong> the<strong> drained butterbeans</strong> and the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the garlic has softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1626787106893-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1626787106893-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1626787106893-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1626787106893-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1626787106893-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, transfer the <strong>butterbeans & garlic</strong> to a <strong>blender</strong>, reserving the pan</p><p>Add the<strong> veg stock</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your<strong> 'creamy' sauce</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1626787128859-x200.jpg",
