            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, tear the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> straight into the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to brown</p><p>Add the<strong> remaining butterbeans</strong> and the<strong> gnocchi</strong> and cook for a further 5-6 min or until everything is starting to crisp</p>",
